            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Joshua.7:16-9:2",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJoshua%207%3A16-9%3A2%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_16%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EAchan%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Sin%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EEarly%20the%20next%20morning%20Joshua%20brought%20the%20tribes%20of%20Israel%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20tribe%20of%20Judah%20was%20singled%20out.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_17%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20clans%20of%20Judah%20came%20forward%2C%20and%20the%20clan%20of%20Zerah%20was%20singled%20out.%20Then%20the%20families%20of%20Zerah%20came%20forward%2C%20and%20the%20family%20of%20Zimri%20was%20singled%20out.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_18%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EEvery%20member%20of%20Zimri%26%23x2019%3Bs%20family%20was%20brought%20forward%20person%20by%20person%2C%20and%20Achan%20was%20singled%20out.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_19%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Joshua%20said%20to%20Achan%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20son%2C%20give%20glory%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20by%20telling%20the%20truth.%20Make%20your%20confession%20and%20tell%20me%20what%20you%20have%20done.%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20hide%20it%20from%20me.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_20%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EAchan%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%20is%20true!%20I%20have%20sinned%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_21%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EAmong%20the%20plunder%20I%20saw%20a%20beautiful%20robe%20from%20Babylon%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A21a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EShinar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20200%26%23xA0%3Bsilver%20coins%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A21b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E200%26%23xA0%3Bshekels%20of%20silver%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%205%26%23xA0%3Bpounds%20or%202.3%26%23xA0%3Bkilograms%20in%20weight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20a%20bar%20of%20gold%20weighing%20more%20than%20a%20pound.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A21c%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E50%26%23xA0%3Bshekels%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%2020%26%23xA0%3Bounces%20or%20570%26%23xA0%3Bgrams%20in%20weight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20I%20wanted%20them%20so%20much%20that%20I%20took%20them.%20They%20are%20hidden%20in%20the%20ground%20beneath%20my%20tent%2C%20with%20the%20silver%20buried%20deeper%20than%20the%20rest.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_22%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Joshua%20sent%20some%20men%20to%20make%20a%20search.%20They%20ran%20to%20the%20tent%20and%20found%20the%20stolen%20goods%20hidden%20there%2C%20just%20as%20Achan%20had%20said%2C%20with%20the%20silver%20buried%20beneath%20the%20rest.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_23%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20took%20the%20things%20from%20the%20tent%20and%20brought%20them%20to%20Joshua%20and%20all%20the%20Israelites.%20Then%20they%20laid%20them%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_24%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Joshua%20and%20all%20the%20Israelites%20took%20Achan%2C%20the%20silver%2C%20the%20robe%2C%20the%20bar%20of%20gold%2C%20his%20sons%2C%20daughters%2C%20cattle%2C%20donkeys%2C%20sheep%2C%20goats%2C%20tent%2C%20and%20everything%20he%20had%2C%20and%20they%20brought%20them%20to%20the%20valley%20of%20Achor.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_25%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Joshua%20said%20to%20Achan%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhy%20have%20you%20brought%20trouble%20on%20us%3F%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20now%20bring%20trouble%20on%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%20And%20all%20the%20Israelites%20stoned%20Achan%20and%20his%20family%20and%20burned%20their%20bodies.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_7_26%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20piled%20a%20great%20heap%20of%20stones%20over%20Achan%2C%20which%20remains%20to%20this%20day.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20place%20has%20been%20called%20the%20Valley%20of%20Trouble%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A26%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Evalley%20of%20Achor.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20ever%20since.%20So%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20no%20longer%20angry.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_1%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJoshua%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Israelites%20Defeat%20Ai%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Joshua%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BDo%20not%20be%20afraid%20or%20discouraged.%20Take%20all%20your%20fighting%20men%20and%20attack%20Ai%2C%20for%20I%20have%20given%20you%20the%20king%20of%20Ai%2C%20his%20people%2C%20his%20town%2C%20and%20his%20land.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_2%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20will%20destroy%20them%20as%20you%20destroyed%20Jericho%20and%20its%20king.%20But%20this%20time%20you%20may%20keep%20the%20plunder%20and%20the%20livestock%20for%20yourselves.%20Set%20an%20ambush%20behind%20the%20town.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_3%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Joshua%20and%20all%20the%20fighting%20men%20set%20out%20to%20attack%20Ai.%20Joshua%20chose%2030%2C000%20of%20his%20best%20warriors%20and%20sent%20them%20out%20at%20night%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_4%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3Ewith%20these%20orders%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BHide%20in%20ambush%20close%20behind%20the%20town%20and%20be%20ready%20for%20action.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_5%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20our%20main%20army%20attacks%2C%20the%20men%20of%20Ai%20will%20come%20out%20to%20fight%20as%20they%20did%20before%2C%20and%20we%20will%20run%20away%20from%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_6%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20will%20let%20them%20chase%20us%20until%20we%20have%20drawn%20them%20away%20from%20the%20town.%20For%20they%20will%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20Israelites%20are%20running%20away%20from%20us%20as%20they%20did%20before.%26%23x2019%3B%20Then%2C%20while%20we%20are%20running%20from%20them%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_7%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3Eyou%20will%20jump%20up%20from%20your%20ambush%20and%20take%20possession%20of%20the%20town%2C%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20will%20give%20it%20to%20you.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_8%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ESet%20the%20town%20on%20fire%2C%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20commanded.%20You%20have%20your%20orders.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_9%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20they%20left%20and%20went%20to%20the%20place%20of%20ambush%20between%20Bethel%20and%20the%20west%20side%20of%20Ai.%20But%20Joshua%20remained%20among%20the%20people%20in%20the%20camp%20that%20night.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_10%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EEarly%20the%20next%20morning%20Joshua%20roused%20his%20men%20and%20started%20toward%20Ai%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20elders%20of%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_11%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20the%20fighting%20men%20who%20were%20with%20Joshua%20marched%20in%20front%20of%20the%20town%20and%20camped%20on%20the%20north%20side%20of%20Ai%2C%20with%20a%20valley%20between%20them%20and%20the%20town.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_12%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThat%20night%20Joshua%20sent%20about%205%2C000%20men%20to%20lie%20in%20ambush%20between%20Bethel%20and%20Ai%2C%20on%20the%20west%20side%20of%20the%20town.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_13%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20they%20stationed%20the%20main%20army%20north%20of%20the%20town%20and%20the%20ambush%20west%20of%20the%20town.%20Joshua%20himself%20spent%20that%20night%20in%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_14%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20king%20of%20Ai%20saw%20the%20Israelites%20across%20the%20valley%2C%20he%20and%20all%20his%20army%20hurried%20out%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20attacked%20the%20Israelites%20at%20a%20place%20overlooking%20the%20Jordan%20Valley.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A14%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Arabah.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20But%20he%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20realize%20there%20was%20an%20ambush%20behind%20the%20town.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_8_15%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EJoshua%20and%20the%20Israelite%20army%20fled%20toward%20the%20wilderness%20as%20though%20they%20were%20badly%20beaten.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%